title: Grateful Dead Live at The Spectrum on 1987-09-22
description:
Set 1

Hey Pocky Way, Althea, Little Red Rooster, When Push Comes To Shove, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Ramble On Rose, Addam's Family, Cassidy, Deal

Set 2

Gimme Some Lovin'*, China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Samson & Delilah-> Terrapin Station-> Drums-> Jam-> The Wheel-> Truckin'-> Stella Blue-> Sugar Magnolia, E: It's All Over Now Baby Blue

* with Spencer Davis

reviews.review_text: My daughter's first I took my 10yo daughter to it for her first concert. I still have the pocket notebook she used to record the set list and make her sketches -- likes of smiling faces and twirling figures. So, while it wasn't the greatest show ever, it still is the best I ever attended.
